node.text:
Texas gubernatorial candidate, LTC Allen West discusses the walkout by Texas State Democrats, and the need to hold our legislators accountable.

node.text:
Folks, we have a real crisis at our border. We shot this footage at 1AM in the border town of Roma, Texas. Please watch and share.

Leaders go to the frontlines to assess a problem. Leaders lead 24/7, being a governor is not a 9-5 job. 

This crisis at our border is one of the reasons I am fighting for you. Will you join me in Defending the Texas Republic?

node.text: I have often said that small business are the economic engine of these United States. As I travel the state, I will be highlighting these tremendous business owners. First up, Buddy's in Ingram, TX. #smallbusiness #smallbusinessowner #ingramtx #texas #texasfirst #west4texas
